OL,5, Network Rail has made workers a fresh  
OL,6, pay offer in an attempt to to break a  
OL,7, deadlocked row with unions over pay,   
OL,8, jobs and conditions.                   
OL,10,FThousands of Network Rail workers took 
OL,11,Fpart in national strike action in June.
OL,13,FIt said the offer was worth more than  
OL,14,F5%, but depended on workers accepting  
OL,15,F"modernising reforms".                 
OL,17,FBut the RMT union said the offer was a 
OL,18,Freal terms pay cut and would mean      
OL,19,Fcutting a third of front-line          
OL,20,Fmaintenance roles.                     
